表的代码预览购置

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('enprise') and o.name = 'FK_ENPRISE_ENPRISE_ENTERPRI')
alter table enprise
drop constraint FK_ENPRISE_ENPRISE_ENTERPRI
go

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('enprise') and o.name = 'FK_ENPRISE_ENPRISE2_FACTORY')
alter table enprise
drop constraint FK_ENPRISE_ENPRISE2_FACTORY
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('enprise')
and name = 'enprise_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index enprise.enprise_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('enprise')
and name = 'enprise2_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index enprise.enprise2_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('enprise')
and type = 'U')
drop table enprise
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: enprise */
/*==============================================================*/
create table enprise (
eno char(8) not null,
fno char(10) not null,
constraint PK_ENPRISE primary key nonclustered (eno, fno)
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: enprise2_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index enprise2_FK on enprise (
fno ASC
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: enprise_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index enprise_FK on enprise (
eno ASC
)
go

alter table enprise
add constraint FK_ENPRISE_ENPRISE_ENTERPRI foreign key (eno)
references enterprise (eno)
go

alter table enprise
add constraint FK_ENPRISE_ENPRISE2_FACTORY foreign key (fno)
references factory (fno)
go
